tton vt-p\" href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/throne-personal-blogmagazine-wordpress-theme/8134834\">Purchase Throne theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Chronicle theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/chronicle-premium-theme/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/chronicle.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Chronicle is a Full Responsive Multi-Purpose Theme suitable for Business , corporate office and others. Cool Blog Layout and full width page also present.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://weblizar.com/themes/chronicle-premium-theme/\">Purchase Chronicle theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Shopera theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/shopera/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/shopera.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Shopera is FREE, clean, modern, responsive and highly customizable WooCommerce theme. It’s perfect for any kind of web shop. It looks great with all types of devices (laptops, tablets and mobiles).</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/shopera/\">Download Shopera theme</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=LmjfEfXr88o:ADFtyxv3NLE:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=LmjfEfXr88o:ADFtyxv3NLE:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=LmjfEfXr88o:ADFtyxv3NLE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=LmjfEfXr88o:ADFtyxv3NLE:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://