eady Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Multilingual Ready Plugins \" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title=\"Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins\" href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">rtDating theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/rtdating/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/rtdating.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Unique, clean and modern theme useful for dating sites and community website.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://rtcamp.com/products/rtdating/\" target=\"_blank\">Purchase rtDating theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Altea theme</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.little-neko.com/portfolio-item/altea-one-page-wordpress-theme/\"><img src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/altea.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Altea is lightweight, one-page, multi-purpose WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://www.little-neko.com/portfolio-item/altea-one-page-wordpress-theme/\">Purchase Altea theme</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Follow my Blog Post plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/follow-my-blog-post-wordpress-plugin/6107586\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/follow.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin allows your users to follow changes on a particular post/page for your WordPress site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"http://codecanyon.net/item/follow-my-blog-post-wordpress-plugin/6107586\">Purchase Follow my Blog Post Plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Immonex OpenImmo2WP plugin</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://plugins.inveris.de/shop/immonex-openimmo2wp/\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493\" src=\"https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/immonex.png\" alt=\"ekho\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin is a lightweight solution for importing and frequently updating OpenImmo XML real estate data into WordPress sites based on various popular themes</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://plugins.inveris.de/shop/immonex-openimmo2wp/\">Purchase Immonex OpenImmo2WP plugin</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=gUdooiXuF_g:CQSDaKe2lFo:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=gUdooiXuF_g:CQSDaKe2lFo:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=gUdooiXuF_g:CQSDaKe2lFo:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=gUdooiXuF_g:CQSDaKe2lFo:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> 